Dorothy Hawtree https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Hawtree 0 Dorothy Hawtree was an Australian model and actor during the Silent era. Her beauty saw her become a model for Rexona soap. She retired on her marriage but later divorced. Dorothy_Hawtree was an_Australian_model_and_actor during the_Silent_era . Her_beauty saw her become a_model for Rexona_soap .
